latestPosts.caption: Honoured that he’s always reachable to us @pinarayivijayan I met him after so many years, the care and warmth that he used to show towards me when I was child was still there. I din feel like I was standing next to the Chief Minister of Kerala I felt like I was talking to Pinarayi uncle who used to live next door. I’m fortunate enough to have lunch with him and I used talk to him whenever I saw him arriving. All those days little did I knew I was talking to or sitting next to the Future CM of Kerala. I am so happy that our CM still has that affection towards us then & now. Happy happy Onam ❤️
